OL,3,CTwo bodies buried in wrong graves at
OL,4,Ccemetery
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway after the
OL,7,Fbodies of two people were buried in
OL,8,Fthe wrong plots at a cemetery in
OL,9,FHampshire.
OL,11,FThe incident at the Bishopstoke
OL,12,FCemetery in Southampton was reported
OL,13,Fto the parish council on 2 February.
OL,15,FThe families and loved ones of those
OL,16,Finvolved have been informed.
OL,18,FThe council says it is working with
OL,19,Fthem to determine how to move forward
OL,20,Fto rectify the situation and make sure
OL,21,Fit does not happen again.
