OL,6,F"The Council is determined to address
OL,7,Fthis as quickly as possible so that
OL,8,Fall concerned can have the comfort
OL,9,Fthey deserve in knowing their loved
OL,10,Fones are in their permanent resting
OL,11,Fplace.
OL,13,F"Once the investigation is complete
OL,14,Fthen its recommendations will be
OL,15,Fconsidered by the Council, and
OL,16,Fmeasures will be adopted to ensure
OL,17,Fthat this does not happen again.
OL,19,F"Our deepest sympathies go to all
OL,20,Fthose affected by this unfortunate
OL,21,Fsituation."
